videos.description: Allonzo Trier gets Arizona out early with the steal and the layup.
videos.headline: Arizona's Trier gets the steal and finishes the layup on the break

videos.description: With UCLA running the fast break, Lonzo Ball puts on a sweet spin move and dishes to TJ Leaf for the dunk.
videos.headline: TJ Leaf gets the nice pass from Lonzo Ball and finishes with a dunk

videos.description: UCLA's Ike Anigbogu rises up with the huge rejection and Lonzo Ball finishes the layup with his left hand plus the foul.
videos.headline: Anigbogu's huge block leads to and-1 layup for  Ball

videos.description: Lonzo Ball has his eyes on the ball. Getting the steal and making the layup.
videos.headline: Lonzo Ball with the steal and the layup

videos.description: Allonzo Trier goes from end to end and splits the defense for the layup plus the foul for Arizona.
videos.headline: Allonzo Trier goes coast-to-coast for the nice and-1 layup

videos.description: Aaron Holiday gets the steal and is able to confuse the defender before hammering it home for UCLA.
videos.headline: UCLA's Holiday gets the steal, fakes out defender and jams it home

videos.description: Allonzo Trier getting passed three defenders and goes up and under to make the layup.
videos.headline: Allonzo Trier makes layup over three Bruins

videos.description: Arizona head coach Sean Miller happy with his team having the lead at half and the spank Keanu Pinder provided.
videos.headline: Arizona head coach Sean Miller happy with his team having the lead at half

videos.description: Arizona's  Rawle Alkins drives and jams home the dunk as the UCLA defenders get out of the way.
videos.headline: Arizona's Alkins drives throws down emphatic dunk

videos.description: TJ Leaf gets past the defender and slams it down.
videos.headline: TJ Leaf driving down for the slam

videos.description: Arizona's Kadeem Allen air balls the potential game tying 3-pointer as they lose to UCLA.
videos.headline: Arizona shoots air ball as they cant hit game tying 3-pointer

videos.description: UCLA Head Coach Steve Alford and Freshman Lonzo Ball discusses the big win.
videos.headline: Post-game interview with Steve Alford and Lonzo Ball

videos.description: Jay Bilas breaks down UCLA's 77-72 win over Arizona in which the Bruins recorded 14 offensive rebounds and were able to set up opportunities for second-chance points.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Analysis (Bilas credits UCLA's ability to rebound for victory) 2017/02/25 SC

videos.headline: Bilas credits UCLA's ability to rebound for victory
